videos.headline: Barkley's 3-yard TD run gives Penn State early lead
videos.description: Penn State RB Saquon Barkley runs up the gut three yards into the end zone to give Penn State the lead.

videos.headline: Markell Jones run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.description: Markell Jones run for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: David Blough pass to Cameron Posey for 1 yd for a TD to give Purdue the lead
videos.description: David Blough pass complete to Cameron Posey for 1 yd for a TD

videos.headline: Penn State's McSorley finds Godwin for 38-yard touchdown
videos.description: Trace McSorley completes a short pass to Chris Godwin and Godwin does the rest going 38 yards for the Penn State touchdown to even the score at 14 against Purdue.

videos.headline: David Blough pass intercepted by Brandon Smith
videos.description: David Blough pass intercepted Brandon Smith return for 22 yds to the Prdue 24

videos.headline: McSorley and Godwin connect for second TD of game for Penn State
videos.description: Trace McSorley throws his second touchdown pass of the day to Chris Godwin to put No. 24 Penn State out in front of Purdue 24-17.

videos.headline: Barkley bursts down the sideline for 81-yard TD
videos.description: Penn State RB Saquon Barkley bounces off a defender before charging up the sideline past Purdue's defense and into the end zone for an 81-yard touchdown, the longest rushing touchdown of his career.
